review_en: I moved around and looked for a place nearby first. I think Sambo here is the perfect place to go with the children. I like the facilities and the price, and above all, the employees are so kind that I went bowling happily. Oh, my God! I've discovered a whole new world. I was so busy raising my kids that I got together with my college classmates and they're all relieved of their stress!I made an appointment to see you again next month. It's been a while since I had so much fun!!!LOL I'm right in front of my house, so I play bowling a lot with my friends for fun. The boss is kind and now I go there often, so I think I go there more often because they recognize me as a regular customer. I'm having a good time every time I go there often with my friends, and the facilities are so nice.lol lol lol I think I should go this week.I recommend it. Located in the eastern market of Jungwha-dong.These days, the place is decorated with glow-in-the-dark and has a lot of fun with exciting music. It's a fun place to go bowling, except that it's a little far from my neighborhood. Rock bowling... The reason why I like glow-in-the-dark bowling is because it's exciting and fun. It's near the eastern market and it's good to go with my friends sometimes. It's not close to my neighborhood because it's Myeonmok-dong, but I think it's the best place to go rock bowling! There aren't many rock bowling alley... Oh, I was going to go bowling in Myeonmok-dong a while ago.Why didn't you come here then? I'll be there next time. I was looking for a bowling alley. The music is exciting and shiny. I heard there's a rock bowling alley in Gangnam. I heard that there's a rock bowling alley in Jungnang-gu. It's clean and nice, maybe because it's been refurbished. Shoes are glow-in-the-dark and the sense of spraying Febreze with new ones. I love it.I was wondering if rock bowling was far away and it was glow-in-the-dark bowling? That's how I looked for the glow-in-the-dark bowling alley.I didn't know there was so much information here.I'm going to play soon. I didn't know there was a rock bowling alley in Myeonmok-dong.I'll have to visit you soon. It's rare to find a place like this. I wanted to play field bowling.I was looking for it, and I went... I think it's good to stop by regardless of the time. It's late-night business, so I went after the company dinner...It's so good to go at night!!!!!! Wow!

review_en: It's not like any other room escape. It's so much fun. It was amazing that we chose a character and solved the problem. The staff is kind and very funny!! I didn't want to waste money. The sound, puzzle, and interior are all so real that it's so immersive. It was scary in the middle, but it was fun.Seribrum is fun! I strongly recommend! I'll do something else next time. Unlike other escape rooms, the facilities were clean and it was fun because there were many electronic devices! I strongly recommend it. Although I couldn't escape the room.It was so much fun. The masters are kind and the room is big~ I strongly recommend it! ^^. The devices and structures are amazing! And I saw Hong Jin-ho. He's a successful fan. I've been to a room escape brand. It's been a while since I did well-made room escape. You can choose the level of difficulty, so beginners are okay, but if you've tried it before, just do it. You're an orphan even if you don't eat it! It's so much fun!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!ğŸŒ¿ğŸŒºğŸ€ğŸ€ğŸ€ğŸ€ğŸ€ğŸ€. It's my first time doing room escape with my friends. The quality is better than I thought. The staff members are very kind to explain.^^I should try again with a higher level of difficulty!! It's my first time doing a room escape game. It's so much fun. I want to try it again. Breakoutscape good good. We did room escape three times, and the level of difficulty was flat, but it was so much fun!! I did Hawkers 1 and there is Hawkers 2, so I will definitely come with my friends! It's so much fun that I want to do it as soon as I get the chance. But since it's a reservation system, I'm leaving with tears in my eyes...For those who like the difficult level, it may be easy, so please refer to that.It's fun~~ It's very fun for a couple to come and play. review_en: Tropical fish is basic. Diverse aquatic organisms that are not easily encountered. Indoor aquarium. High quality coffee. A cafe where you can meet hand drips at a good price. A place where about 500 kinds of board games can be played. Pocketball for fun. A mini billiard room with four balls.  A favorite cafe to play board games. The place I often visit to play board games!  It's been a long time since I've been there.   I enjoyed Agricola, Winners Circle, Las Vegas, and Tichu.   I don't think it's a bad idea to ask you to recommend games to match the number of people who went with you for the first time.    I was recommended by Mr. Aza, so I got to know some famous games such as Powergrid and Abyss. There are a lot of guppies and other unique marine life in the aquarium. I used to go to Sillim-dong Board School often, but I couldn't find the board game I was looking for, so I came here to see if there was any... There were even more fun games than that. The boss is good at recommending games. After playing a hard game, I counted the number of games during the break, and I counted it to 750 haha. The price here is cheap, the boss is kind and funny, and I love it. *^^*

review_en: There are two part-timers, and they arrived 10 minutes ago, but they can't wait. They told me to wait outside, so I shivered outside on a cold day and canceled; I couldn't let them sit inside even though there was a seat. -- I don't like it. Quality....Lee Ha-im. No logic. I'm getting the answer. How absurd? I don't know what the logic is.You're paying me for this? Whether it's the concept or the original, the smell of the sewer is so unpleasant. I found the key, but it didn't work, so I wasted a lot of time. In conclusion, it's not funny. There's only one hint for three. There's no more.There are some people who try to add a hint, and I asked them to give me a hint because it's a difficult step, and they said it's like asking for the right answer. Even if it's just a rule, it takes a few minutes because there is no important UV lamp battery inside; the connection between the problems seems to be a little off. It would be better to have more room escape cafes at Jonggak. The owner is very rude and boring. I couldn't help but write when I didn't write anything like this.I played room escape game in Daehangno before and it was fun so I went here and lost 40,000 won. There's no probability in the story.'Ha' came out with a feeling of mystery.

review_en: First of all, the female counter staff is so unfriendly and she gets caught twice, and every time she protests, she scolds her eyes and says something. I felt really bad. I wish there was another bowling alley in this town. There's only this place, so people are flocking here. Do you really hate to pay for the quality of the wait for more than an hour of waiting? The female counter staff was very unfriendly and there were a few broken balls. And there was a phenomenon where bowling pins were not able to fall over alone due to machine errors, but the score was added. My team is really bad at bowling, so they're getting angry because I'm getting caught on the rails. I've been here a lot so far, and my parents are asking me to pay 50 million won for my team member.  Who do you think you're a fool? You're such a junkie here that you want to make personal attacks on female employees.                                 It's annoying to see the female staff frowning every time they come to the bowling alley on a regular basis. They're coming every two weeks. Do you think we're making a big fuss? I'm telling you, if you don't hire two of your staff, you're doomed. I want to give you a zero rating.Folding. Can't you lower than 2 points? The service is terrible.I rolled it once or twice to see if you didn't clean the lane, and your hands were black and some balls were broken, but you don't seem to be taking care of them.The facilities are completely old-fashioned. They're sunny.I love you, pretty girl.

review_en: Aside from the game, the boss is very unfriendly. I arrived before the reservation time, and he was telling me that I was really late, that I was late, that if I didn't start now, I'd be late, so I'd have to explain it roughly and start. The room actually comes out in 30 minutes. I was underdeveloped, but I had a lot of fun. This is the least interesting place I've ever been to... I heard that the automatic device is 80 percent, but it's not... I don't know if it's because there's no one working, but even if I ask for a hint, they don't respond right away and I can It was even dark, so there was no problem, and there was a malfunction...  It's not a place to go in anticipation of the story. It was close to money. I'm addicted to escape room cafes. Exodus Hongdae was the best. We've tried everything from the level of difficulty to the level of award. As if you're back to your childhood at the Olympics, the game is so fun and you should try to escape the zombies. It's so much fun! It was the worst room escape I've ever been to in Hongdae. The male staff explained it to me at first, and all the people I went to, including me, felt that he spoke too fast and roughly. So I couldn't understand two-thirds of the explanation. The escape room cafe was an important part of the explanation, but it was so disappointing that the problem was less connected than other escape cafes, so there were many parts where it was disconnected whether it was right or what to do next. It's 17,000 won even if you get a double cash discount or a good discount, but it's not that cheap and I don't want to recommend it. Compared to other room escape cafes that offer social discounts, it's really bad.Folding
